### ============================================
### Payment Service 테스트 (8083)
### ============================================

### 1. 결제 생성
POST http://localhost:8083/api/payments?orderId=1&amount=30000&paymentMethod=CARD
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. 결제 조회 (ID)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/payments/1

### 3. 결제 조회 (주문 ID)
GET http://localhost:8083/api/payments/by-order/1

### 4. 결제 승인
POST http://localhost:8083/api/payments/1/approve

### 5. 결제 확정
POST http://localhost:8083/api/payments/1/confirm

### 6. 결제 환불
POST http://localhost:8083/api/payments/1/refund
